    "crt:notes": "VHF Nutrition instance v1.0.0. Six B2C/B2B2C consumer archetypes. Dietitian role (B2B2C_Intermediary) connects downstream to multiple B2C consumer segments. Health Investor role reflects longevity/biohacking segment premium opportunity. Parent/Carer role captures family nutrition purchasing with budget-sensitive profile distinct from personal-use consumers."
  }
